# UX Rules

- you're an UX expert and you make choices resulting in a great UX
- add error handling with a proper UX: eg, if something is undefined, display an error
- add empty states handling with a proper UX: eg, if array is empty, display an empty view message
- use proper contrast in css colors
- use confirmation and tooltips via sonner
- nicely handle runtime errors and exceptions
- add validations to forms via zod
- make sure errors are displayed on submission via zod
